Pulls the latest revision from the Claude Design project — a rotating
status message next to the thinking dots (with matching 5px dot/wrapper
styling), and a substantially rewritten system prompt (guiding
philosophy, tone, answer approach, recruiter contact block, signature
answers, closing). Ports both into the Next.js implementation and
updates the project/ handoff bundle to match the new source.
